6.showMessage?topicID=176.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showMessage?topicID=171.topic"> Next Topic >> </a> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0 width=95%><tr><td bgcolor=#000000><table border=0 width=100% cellpadding=5 cellspacing=1><tr><td valign=top bgcolor=#cc9966 class=headings><font color=#FFFFFF>Author</font></td><td valign=top bgcolor=#cc9966 class=headings><font color=#FFFFFF>Comment</font></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ubarmaidmeg.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Barmaid Meg</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 1<br> <font color=#993300>(7/12/01 7:54:59 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=170.topic>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Just Visiting</span><hr size=1> She stopped in the Amazon Territory, huffing and puffing. It had seemed to be forever since she had been the lands, she looked around, hoping they remembered just who she was, she didn't feel like dodging arrows today. It had been months she she had last seen Morpheus, and....he thought he was never going to come back. She was lonely, it gets lonely in the big old place by itself. No children to keep her company, they were all grown...stupid Immortal gene, making her kids grow up fast! She continued to trudge down the path, but stopped...er...which way was it again? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> Cyane Kinneas</span><br> <span class=usertitle>Unregistered User</span><br>   <font color=#993300>(7/12/01 1:10:58 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=170.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> A long lost mother. . .</span><hr size=1> Cyane had followed Meg all the way from Ephesus. She stopped once they reached the Scynthian village.<br>
Cyane caught up with her mother and looked at the gates.<br>
<br>
&quot;Scynthia. . .? I've heard of this village before. My old tribe said that the Queen here was kind to neighboring tribes. . .&quot; She looked up at her mother.<br>
<br>
&quot;Do you know the Queen here?&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ubarmaidmeg.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Barmaid Meg</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#993300>(7/29/01 11:02:57 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=170.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A long lost mother. . .</span><hr size=1> She jumped, Cyane's presence startling her, she really needed to know when people were following her to save her from having a heart attack!<br>
<br>
&quot;Yes, I know the Queen here.&quot; She smiled. &quot;She's a friend of the families.&quot;<br>
<br>
Indeed, Alysia was! All that business way back when before they found out who Sayler's mother really was, they had been family. She still felt that way toward them, and she would forever. It would be good to see someone close to family again.<br>
<br>
&quot;I could introduce you...&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uamazonbelle.showPublicProfile?language=EN>AmazonBelle</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 4<br> <font color=#993300>(7/30/01 12:49:31 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=170.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A long lost mother. . .</span><hr size=1> Belle smiled a bit as she walked from her hut and approached the gates, spotting Cyane and her mother.<br>
<br>
&quot;I just can't go anywhere without seeing you, can I?&quot;<br>
<br>
She spoke with an overdramatic sigh then a grin to her friend.<br>
<br>
&quot;Well? Introduce me. This is your mother, right?&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ubarmaidmeg.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Barmaid Meg</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 3<br> <font color=#993300>(7/30/01 3:02:28 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=170.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A long lost mother. . .</span><hr size=1> She looked to Belle, and gave her that infamous Meg smile, and offered a hand to her.<br>
<br>
"Name's Meg." She looked to Cyane, then back to Belle. "You know her, Cy?" <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> Cyane Ephiny Kinneas</span><br> <span class=usertitle>Unregistered User</span><br>   <font color=#993300>(7/30/01 3:58:12 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=170.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> A Long Lost Mother</span><hr size=1> Cyane shook her head to her mothers question.<br>
<br>
&quot;No need mother, I already know Queen Alysia.&quot;<br>
<br>
She saw Belle and smirked walking over giving her a hug. Her eyes turned back to her mother who was standing there.<br>
<br>
&quot;Know her? Of course I know her. She's only my best friend in the whole world.&quot;<br>
<br>
Cyane smirked and once again turned back to her mother.<br>
<br>
&quot;I go to school with her and Wulf.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uamazonbelle.showPublicProfile?language=EN>AmazonBelle</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 5<br> <font color=#993300>(7/30/01 5:17:25 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=170.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A Long Lost Mother</span><hr size=1> Belle gave her friend a hug then shook Meg's hand with a smile.<br>
<br>
&quot;I'm Belle Loire. It's nice to meet you.&quot;<br>
<br>
She took a step back and smiled towards the two of them.<br>
<br>
&quot;So, what are you guys doing here?&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ubarmaidmeg.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Barmaid Meg</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 4<br> <font color=#993300>(7/30/01 5:18:47 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=170.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> School? ...Wow.</span><hr size=1> School? How proud she was! One of her children actually goes to school! The other's learned from their father...which wasn't very  much. <br>
<br>
"School? Well.." She smiled. "It's good to know you have friends, Cy." She looked around again, then back to them. "And you know Aly, huh?" <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uamazonbelle.showPublicProfile?language=EN>AmazonBelle</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 6<br> <font color=#993300>(7/30/01 6:37:08 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=170.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Scool? ...Wow.</span><hr size=1> Belle laughed lightly with a nod.<br>
<br>
&quot;She spends too much time around me not to know Aly by now.&quot;<br>
<br>
She gave another nod as if to confirm what she was saying. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> Cyane Ephiny Kinneas</span><br> <span class=usertitle>Unregistered User</span><br>   <font color=#993300>(7/31/01 1:43:51 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=170.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Smirks. . .</span><hr size=1> Cyane smirked lightly.<br>
<br>
&quot;You haven't been to Scynthia in a long time have you mom?&quot;<br>
<br>
She smirked looking to Belle and then back to Meg.<br>
<br>
&quot;This is Belle Loire, Princess of Scynthia. Alysia's Daughter.&quot;<br>
<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ubarmaidmeg.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Barmaid Meg</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 5<br> <font color=#993300>(7/31/01 12:32:50 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=170.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Daughter?</span><hr size=1> She shook her head, giggling<br>
<br>
"It's been a while." <br>
<br>
She blinked. Daughter? <br>
<br>
"Daughter? Wow. Nice to meet you."<br>
<br>
She smiled. Meg wasn't too formal when it came to meeting any kind of royalty, she was never raised in that. So, she really didn't call people by their "proper" titles. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uamazonbelle.showPublicProfile?language=EN>AmazonBelle</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 7<br> <font color=#993300>(7/31/01 12:56:54 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=170.topic&index=11>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Daughter?</span><hr size=1> Belle laughed a bit with a nod.<br>
<br>
&quot;Adopted daughter. And it's nice to meet you two.&quot;<br>
<br>
She smiled. She didn't even notice Meg wasn't being formal. She didn't like titles anyway. Her name was long enough without the titles added on. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showMessage?topicID=176.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showMessage?topicID=171.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=170.topic&index=11><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.emailToFriend?topicID=170.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.threadControl?topicID=170.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=170.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=170.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub11.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="amazonsuniteamazonsunitescrollboard">Amazons Unite Scroll Board<option value="amazonsunitefrm23">The Olympian Gods<option value="amazonsunitefrm15">Black Sea